x4freetext: In the experiments, the self-supporting targets of
isotopes 90,92-Zr and 92-Mo made by a method of
electrochemical evaporation have been used.
Isotope:             90-Zr    92-Zr         92-Mo
thickness (mg/cm**2) 2.13      0.8           0.51
enrichment (%)        95       97            95
* EN-RSL
See SAMPLE
For the registration and
identification of reaction products in the whole energy
range, a system has been designed with a
three-detection telescope (DE1-DE2-E3), consisting of
two silicon surface-barrier detectors and a
scintillation detector with a total  absorption.   The
thicknesses of detectors were DE1=50 mumeters, DE2=
5300 mumeters, and E3=25 mm correspondingly.
